cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.HC, cs.NE 

This paper deals with image classification using pre-trained CNNs and machine learning classifiers. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses transfer learning, which is a common technique in machine learning, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of pre-trained CNNs and machine learning classifiers also suggests that the paper could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The application of pain expression recognition in neonates involves human-computer interaction, which could place the paper in cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction). Finally, the paper deals with neonates, which could suggest cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as a possible category.
